Package xxl.core.comparators

Provides some useful additional Comparators based on Comparator.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
ComparableComparator<T extends Comparable<T>> The ComparableComparator uses the compareTo method of a given Comparable object to compare two elements.
Comparators This class provides some useful static methods for dealing with comparators.
DistanceBasedComparator<T> The DistanceBasedComparator compares two objects by determining their distances to a given reference object.
EmbeddingComparator<T> The EmbeddingComparator adds a bound to a given comparator.
FeatureComparator<S,T> The FeatureComparator compares the 'feature's of two given objects.
InverseComparator<T> The InverseComparator inverts the ordering of a given Comparator.
LexicographicalComparator<T> The LexicographicalComparator creates a lexicographical ordering.
 

Package xxl.core.comparators Description

Provides some useful additional Comparators based on Comparator.
